sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as DrogonHttpServer<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as GRPCServerModule<br/>configurable/TCP gRPC
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler<br/>(Bearer Token check)
    participant Model as ModelInstance<br/>(Classical ML)
    participant MPExec as MediaPipeGraphExecutor<br/>(Pipeline Engine)
    participant GenAI as GenAiServable<br/>(LLM Engine)
    participant OVRuntime as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant OVGenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>(Continuous Batching)
    participant Cloud as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: Classical Model Inference (REST)
    Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    Proxy->>REST: Forward (HTTP, plaintext)<br/>Auth validated by proxy
    REST->>Handler: Route request
    Handler->>Handler: isAuthorized() check<br/>(api_key_file if configured)
    Handler->>Model: Inference request
    Model->>OVRuntime: Execute inference
    OVRuntime-->>Model: Prediction result
    Model-->>Handler: Response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>Proxy: HTTP response
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completion (Streaming)
    Client->>Proxy: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    Proxy->>REST: Forward (HTTP, plaintext)
    REST->>Handler: Route to OpenAI handler
    Handler->>MPExec: Dispatch to streaming thread pool
    MPExec->>GenAI: LLM calculator invocation
    GenAI->>GenAI: Jinja2 chat template processing
    GenAI->>OVGenAI: Schedule in continuous batch
    loop Streaming tokens
        OVGenAI-->>GenAI: Generated token
        GenAI-->>MPExec: Token chunk
        MPExec-->>REST: SSE event
        REST-->>Proxy: HTTP SSE chunk
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS SSE chunk
    end

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: gRPC Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>gRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, InsecureCredentials
    gRPC->>Model: KFS inference request
    Model->>OVRuntime: Execute inference
    OVRuntime-->>Model: Result tensors
    Model-->>gRPC: InferResponse
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    activate Model
    Model->>Cloud: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>AWS IAM / Azure Conn String / GCP Creds
    Cloud-->>Model: Model files (encrypted in transit)
    Model->>OVRuntime: Load model from local cache
    deactivate Model

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 5: HuggingFace Model Pull
    activate HFHub
    Note right of HFHub: libgit2 + Git LFS<br/>or GGUF Downloader
    HFHub-->>Model: Model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, HF Token
    deactivate HFHub
